      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone prioritizing mechanical functionality over cosmetic perfection. The exterior exhibits common signs of age, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the cabin shows moderate wear on the upholstery and carpets, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain operational. It has been regularly maintained to ensure it runs well, making it an ideal choice for a daily commuter or a first car.",
